                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-text mb-4">
              Visual Feedback
            </h3>
            <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
              Clear visual cues show valid drop zones, conflicts, and current
              position. Dragging feels natural with smooth animations and
              instant feedback.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
