            <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-text mb-4">
              Smart Conflict Detection and Duration Adjustment
            </h3>
            <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
              CalendHub provides real-time conflict detection while dragging
              appointments. When you move an appointment over occupied time
              slots, visual indicators immediately highlight overlapping
              meetings so you see scheduling conflicts before dropping. This
              prevents double-booking errors that traditional form-based
              scheduling creates when you submit conflicting times without
              realizing overlaps. Duration changes work through edge dragging
              where you grab appointment borders and stretch or shrink meeting
              length visually. This eliminates form fields for start time and
              end time, making duration adjustments feel like physically
              reshaping objects rather than entering abstract time values. All
              changes save automatically with one-click undo available if you
              accidentally move wrong appointment or need to reverse
              adjustments.
            </p>
